data.title: Note de Curs. Nomina
data.meta_description: Note de curs. Nomina.doc - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document discusses morphology and provides an overview of key concepts in morphology and its relationship to other areas of linguistics. It notes that morphology deals with word forms and the combination of morphemes into words and sentences. It discusses the different types of morphology (historical/diachronic, descriptive/synchronic, normative). It also discusses the relationship between morphology and other fields like syntax, lexicology, and grammar.
